{"tid":1476450,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"16/8 波台撳錢P (無1000蚊免問)","createTime":"2019-08-15T22:20:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T02:24:36.000Z","uid":5649,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b4a466be3ddba5031ca87fe2a5c48b81c75b61cd","tid":1476450,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T22:20:20.000Z","msg":"是咁的，今日8月16日我地唔入錢了，去銀行享受囡囡與提款。 <br />\n我地book 了3 間銀行。第一間 中国銀行 , 大陸野來的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i3ibKiX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi3ibKiX.jpg&h=609c1feb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mnbwKkC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmnbwKkC.jpg&h=96820e83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n坐50人的，長唔知幾呎。<br />\n<br />\n另一間, 私伙的匯豐銀行 坐20人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kE0ETdj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkE0ETdj.png&h=0809e3fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cLtrydT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcLtrydT.jpg&h=d988e405&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我中意呢間多d，唔係支那野，寫意d。<br />\n<br />\n重有一間存款專用花旗銀行。<br />\n<br />\n搞手會撳好多100蚊同500蚊。<br />\n<br />\n8月16號 , 7點任何銀行集合<br />\n<br />\n男仔：$1000位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （只限波台手腳，本來想搵埋帝吧班支那仔去，不過銀行話d鄉下仔好撚窮 銀行未必有1000蚊，咁就算了）<br />\n<br />\n女仔：MODEL, 靚女免費撳錢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n普通女仔：唔俾唔撳。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n來吧靚女，識d撳得起$1000換做美金的波台手足吧。<br />\n<br />\np.s. 呢d撳錢活動無得賺，搞手只求打個和，大家開開心心撳返晚。"},{"pid":"c8c2a4352f93c2f02b10ea0623786e6d109d814b","tid":1476450,"uid":5649,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T22:26:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZWCga46.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=htt